        "text": "a plant of peace",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ".” But in all the passages referred to in support of the assertion the fig-tree is associated with the vine. It is difficult, therefore, to see how the vine can be singled out as ",
